{
  "texts": [
    "The data is sourced from the Qizhen medical knowledge base and includes real doctor-patient knowledge Q&A data, as well as instructions constructed from text knowledge based on drugs and diseases.",
    "It is primarily used to enhance the models' accuracy in medical knowledge Q&A and alleviate hallucination phenomena.",
    "• ShenNong TCM Dataset (Wei Zhu and Wang, 2023).",
    "The ShenNong TC-M Dataset is a Chinese medical dataset.",
    "Based on an open-source traditional Chinese medicine knowledge graph, the dataset utilizes the Self-Instruct method to construct instruction data centered around traditional Chinese medicine."
  ]
}